y":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"點解夜晚先黎 仲要冇人知得鬼知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1619517375455a20c53993e2f68c4f8aac61c261","tid":1779772,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"1961b6c80e7660828db6b6d4e33b544fe7cd586d","tid":1779772,"uid":22436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:54:02.000Z","msg":"黑警而家打人鳩捉全部仲變本加厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"3996016ccdfc2ac0f242412d19f9e916332ea851","tid":1779772,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"16aa30e94fffed36106fb6a3a09faa56ec5c79e2","tid":1779772,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"便衣狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"再旺角只會送頭，雖然好唔想用送頭呢兩個字，但事實係每晚都有被捕<br />\n<br />\n小部隊式係大馬路快閃唔再可行<br />\n<br />\n根本就<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該再喺旺角快閃</span><br />\n依家啲狗轉晒策略，多咗好多便衣狗丶一見到有手足聚集就call台，搵狗車喺附近埋伏<br />\n但係我哋仲同以前一樣毫無進步<br />\n<br />\n而家佢係啲熱門地方派便衣狗，你少人快閃嘅話即刻拉<br />\n<br />\n解決方法有兩個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1 唔好再喺過往兩個月玩到熟曬嘅地方快閃堵路，有便衣狗監視<br />\n<br />\n2 人越多便衣狗越難行動，另外因為越來越多車巡，亦要多啲哨兵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e917329b074a5209fe0cd428484fb7836bae472","tid":1779772,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"正視聽<br />\n<br />\n唔係武裝殺狗果d根本唔應該靜靜雞<br />\n快閃裝修有和理非人數掩護減低左好多等險<br />\n<br />\n唔好一刀切叫勇武有行動力既手足地下化，咁做等同邊緣化自己，冇support=高風險"},{"pid":"9199f5dd7e33dcf8f9e1c4c075b60af4ac1f7575","tid":1779772,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb65a038f8813701daa2cf56587cf7a74d27e4b7","tid":1779772,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜拉個細路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"求下你哋唔好再係旺角快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴晚同前晚已經比便衣捉左好幾個<br />\n係未諗到方法之前都唔好再去好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小部隊式係大馬路快閃唔再可行<br />\n<br />\n根本就<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該再喺旺角快閃</span><br />\n依家啲狗轉晒策略，多咗好多便衣狗丶一見到有手足聚集就call台，搵狗車喺附近埋伏<br />\n但係我哋仲同以前一樣毫無進步<br />\n<br />\n而家佢係啲熱門地方派便衣狗，你少人快閃嘅話即刻拉<br />\n<br />\n解決方法有兩個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1 唔好再喺過往兩個月玩到熟曬嘅地方快閃堵路，有便衣狗監視<br />\n<br />\n2 人越多便衣狗越難行動，另外因為越來越多車巡，亦要多啲哨兵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c8c81ac6315eb1d5d24d68b3772aa0963c5758ff","tid":1779772,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1619517375455a20c53993e2f68c4f8aac61c261","tid":1779772,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"唉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"小部隊式係大馬路快閃唔再可行<br />\n<br />\n根本就<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該再喺旺角快閃</span><br />\n依家啲狗轉晒策略，多咗好多便衣狗丶一見到有手足聚集就call台，搵狗車喺附近埋伏<br />\n但係我哋仲同以前一樣毫無進步<br />\n<br />\n而家佢係啲熱門地方派便衣狗，你少人快閃嘅話即刻拉<br />\n<br />\n解決方法有兩個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1 唔好再喺過往兩個月玩到熟曬嘅地方快閃堵路，有便衣狗監視<br />\n<br />\n2 人越多便衣狗越難行動，另外因為越來越多車巡，亦要多啲哨兵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f0ea2e766d3ac4d464af5aabf27efadef536b824","tid":1779772,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cl